text: Rutherford Latham (born 7 September 1954) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics, the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Madrid
